snippet.title: Tainted Grail: Conquest — March 2021 Development Update
snippet.description:
Hi! Sorry for 1080p, only after uploading we've seen some quality issues... But, well, it's a development update so let's say that it's also a work in progress! Anyway, here's a quick video concerning Tainted Grail: Conquest! 

Join our journey through Early Access: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1199030/Tainted_Grail_Conquest/

And our Discord: https://discord.gg/kpAPmxfjn3
